    <entry>
      <title>第十四章 鬼迹崖</title>
      <link href="/2026/07/21/Book-14/14%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E5%9B%9B%E7%AB%A0%20%E9%AC%BC%E8%BF%B9%E5%B4%96/"/>
      <url>/2026/07/21/Book-14/14%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E5%9B%9B%E7%AB%A0%20%E9%AC%BC%E8%BF%B9%E5%B4%96/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- WEREAD_SECTION_START --><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_1_START --><div class="weread-card" data-position="1">  <span class="weread-text">你是和我桃花剑岭一派有仇？不论仇人是谁，你算在我身上便是。</span></div><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_1_END --><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_2_START --><div class="weread-card" data-position="2">  <span class="weread-text">这些事再难，总会有办法。长得丑是生来注定的，没有办法。</span></div><!-- WEREAD_HIGHLIGHT_2_END --><!-- WEREAD_SECTION_END -->]]></content>
      
      
